snippet.textDisplay: Coke Studio Pakistan had a good setup from the beginning with Rohail Hayat. In addition to all superb musicians local and foreign and singers with excellence, the background singers of three especially the two girls have done such an excellent and perfect singing accompaniment throughout all the different male and female main singers whether Sufi singing or classical singing.
